{"tid":36571,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人對朋友/愛情好無感覺？","createTime":"2016-12-12T19:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T13:14:45.000Z","uid":39046,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91614a20df89c67230d3be5be98a7e0acbceaa78","tid":36571,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:21:15.000Z","msg":"同朋友相處開心 我都想同佢地有深刻交流<br />\n但一番到屋企就唔會應wtsapp/隔好耐覆<br />\n覺得好浪費時間<br />\n好憎non stop wtsapp<br />\n我會話朋友對我黎講重要<br />\n但對佢地好無感覺<br />\n久而久之 同某d好朋友疏遠左<br />\n但又唔覺得好可惜<br />\n<br />\n有好多人會對我好 但我乜感覺都無<br />\n什至由一開始覺得好感動<br />\n到宜家只係好怕要回報番佢地d乜<br />\n<br />\n好怕呢種麻目既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人試過？點解決好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5def09e389f643607f9bc261b1945989c475425","tid":36571,"uid":18269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:23:34.000Z","msg":"一樣<br />\n<br />\n無野影響到情緒<br />\n拍唔拍拖都無所謂<br />\n分手都唔會傷心<br />\nwtsapp永遠唔想應機"},{"pid":"58052aca89346fad6361dfd976f997ffdb6222ae","tid":36571,"uid":26723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:25:31.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪太毒"},{"pid":"21ab54628076aeaad392d934c2f6bc3ef835ef1a","tid":36571,"uid":14862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:30:57.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<br />\n有冇朋友都已經冇感覺冇所謂<br />\n可有可無，冇左都唔會覺得可惜"},{"pid":"c06b980e1f8c9bcbe504db43d2cb5b4200aeea99","tid":36571,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一樣<br />\n<br />\n無野影響到情緒<br />\n拍唔拍拖都無所謂<br />\n分手都唔會傷心<br />\nwtsapp永遠唔想應機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我又好想拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想有個我真心鐘意既人係我身邊<br />\n但分左手之後就無/唔識對人心動<br />\n<br />\n試過比人問係咪wtsapp壞左<br />\n我唯有答係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2d04e2dd8df4ce86e269db4e4d2c29b64a6cad","tid":36571,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪太毒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你就毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD人覺得我外向/social type <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e652b2fab9f7f35ae333c83d619c93e4cc8ab9c","tid":36571,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:35:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁<br />\n有冇朋友都已經冇感覺冇所謂<br />\n可有可無，冇左都唔會覺得可惜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當我覺得悶/寂寞/節日既時候<br />\n佢地就會變得重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然 佢地唔開心 我都會想開解佢地<br />\n<br />\n同你一樣 其餘時間好似無乜所謂咁"},{"pid":"bb2c5ea5870150d2acee3c5d5e77b32e014803f5","tid":36571,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:39:00.000Z","msg":"哇直頭講緊自己<br />\n明明睇得出對方係好有心維繫段友<br />\n但自己又懶懶行愛理不到<br />\n對愛情又兒戲覺得有無都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e83517d1bcd1a0034f59b800a8f57b7dc0097ef","tid":36571,"uid":32126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:42:04.000Z","msg":"對拍拖無晒感覺<br />\n以前對愛情嘅憧憬不再<br />\n與其話遇唔到啱嘅人<br />\n其實係無咗心動嘅感覺<br />\n唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cb090e5f7738b39fa63a315cd979b2525c7471","tid":36571,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哇直頭講緊自己<br />\n明明睇得出對方係好有心維繫段友<br />\n但自己又懶懶行愛理不到<br />\n對愛情又兒戲覺得有無都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nExactly<br />\n覺得維持關係好煩<br />\n但自己又想同人地有深刻既情感交流<br />\n好矛盾"},{"pid":"d8f9387bbc84ecb6ddd9067e4ea2f44d2b7ed126","tid":36571,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:42:36.000Z","msg":"咦我都係<br />\n雖然人哋唔開心我一定會努力安慰佢<br />\n但如果係咁傾我最後會頂唔順blue tick <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同好多人嘅友誼都係慢慢淡，自己又冇話點<br />\n愛情呢，成日都想有<br />\n但一有人埋嚟就會一早推開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人解釋下"},{"pid":"5d97563bda4feac0ed2805a5a4426f98b24a34e9","tid":36571,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對拍拖無晒感覺<br />\n以前對愛情嘅憧憬不再<br />\n與其話遇唔到啱嘅人<br />\n其實係無咗心動嘅感覺<br />\n唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n憧憬都仲有<br />\n但真係有幾多個人 對我幾好都好<br />\n完全無心動感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7d10bc1d9e6d6726237ba08e6a733caeddd8b8","tid":36571,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:43:59.000Z","msg":"有d似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有適合既人（朋友/愛情）出現，有心靈交流都好開心<br />\n但平時就好撚怕煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d802db647dcbddc283c3a577f892e33a0209b7f9","tid":36571,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咦我都係<br />\n雖然人哋唔開心我一定會努力安慰佢<br />\n但如果係咁傾我最後會頂唔順blue tick <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同好多人嘅友誼都係慢慢淡，自己又冇話點<br />\n愛情呢，成日都想有<br />\n但一有人埋嚟就會一早推開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人解釋下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打心底裡會唔會覺得孤單？<br />\n<br />\nBtw好多人都相類似既感覺<br />\n有無人分析下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解決"},{"pid":"9304acf2f1bdbcacaf693303ca6ad63205a81eb4","tid":36571,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哇直頭講緊自己<br />\n明明睇得出對方係好有心維繫段友<br />\n但自己又懶懶行愛理不到<br />\n對愛情又兒戲覺得有無都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nExactly<br />\n覺得維持關係好煩<br />\n但自己又想同人地有深刻既情感交流<br />\n好矛盾</blockquote><br />\n睇黎都係心底裏想不勞而獲<br />\n想自己唔付出又得到人地既關心掛<br />\n但無呢樣野又覺得問題不大所以搞成咁"},{"pid":"0bc59bf453f9d14e872487f1e625a75b6013eff1","tid":36571,"uid":14862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係咁<br />\n有冇朋友都已經冇感覺冇所謂<br />\n可有可無，冇左都唔會覺得可惜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當我覺得悶/寂寞/節日既時候<br />\n佢地就會變得重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然 佢地唔開心 我都會想開解佢地<br />\n<br />\n同你一樣 其餘時間好似無乜所謂咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n悶/寂寞已經慣曬<br />\n連&quot;想搵人陪&quot;既想法都冇<br />\n不過佢地約我出黎都會出既"},{"pid":"72aa580e221e3f8fe6b9ff279ec323be8eeac419","tid":36571,"uid":28275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:51:43.000Z","msg":"你對人好，人未必對你好<br />\n所以對自己好就可以"},{"pid":"4bfbb44dd0f59453a42950b6d383f119644475ad","tid":36571,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:53:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咦我都係<br />\n雖然人哋唔開心我一定會努力安慰佢<br />\n但如果係咁傾我最後會頂唔順blue tick <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同好多人嘅友誼都係慢慢淡，自己又冇話點<br />\n愛情呢，成日都想有<br />\n但一有人埋嚟就會一早推開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人解釋下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打心底裡會唔會覺得孤單？<br />\n<br />\nBtw好多人都相類似既感覺<br />\n有無人分析下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解決</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔使解決<br />\n同埋坦白講<br />\n我連安慰人都覺得好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5954d6c40fda9c3f3e20345f3aa0106b9769c586","tid":36571,"uid":10733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T20:17:54.000Z","msg":"分左手之後好似有社交恐懼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc4a838fc918163fe7277da7911f49438b97366","tid":36571,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T20:33:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咦我都係<br />\n雖然人哋唔開心我一定會努力安慰佢<br />\n但如果係咁傾我最後會頂唔順blue tick <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同好多人嘅友誼都係慢慢淡，自己又冇話點<br />\n愛情呢，成日都想有<br />\n但一有人埋嚟就會一早推開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人解釋下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打心底裡會唔會覺得孤單？<br />\n<br />\nBtw好多人都相類似既感覺<br />\n有無人分析下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解決</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔使解決<br />\n同埋坦白講<br />\n我連安慰人都覺得好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n安慰人就一時時啦，睇咩心情，冇你咁誇<br />\n可能我啲朋友都係鐘意啲空間，所以同佢哋相處得唔錯<br />\n但通常最唔開心都自己ko<br />\n有時候會覺得孤單，但又會諗好正常邊個唔孤單"},{"pid":"08fc8c2f863e9c32792c0e371f68b173ec64d74c","tid":36571,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T20:53:55.000Z","msg":"有frd係咁<br />\n明明出街山長水遠都肯出<br />\n<br />\n但一分開左就好冷淡<br />\nwtsapp藍剔唔應機，哦嗯哈哈<br />\n對frd好似冇乜感覺咁，佢同佢再之前既朋友都係冇聯絡所以散<br />\n<br />\n成日都想大把大把車埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我好想可以做成世朋友"},{"pid":"b3e42445b9187313bbaddd16b6c3c7e3747eb644","tid":36571,"uid":29737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T23:58:55.000Z","msg":"對愛情係咁，分手後開始無感覺，付出無回饋過一次後驚再係咁<br />\n但友情唔係，give同take都好開心，容易大量d不求回報，可能係因為感覺無咁強烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f31f0a81434c12e468c52f60c7ae91ace869a9b","tid":36571,"uid":28792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:28:45.000Z","msg":"搵到答案了多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9ba3c8be9ad204fe419c63057f6b03f9d49493","ti