/></blockquote><br />\n都係"},{"pid":"7bed55715ef9dec039bb35690232e79cad1d51e0","tid":36571,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對人冇感情就冇感情啦 你冇左朋友都唔覺得可惜 係代表你心底入面冇重視過人 上面有啲人仲扮乜嘢社交恐懼又話自己毒呀 多多藉口 你唔重視 唔珍惜人地 到有一日你遇見一個你好重視嘅人 果個人都同樣唔會珍惜你 覺得你只係可有可無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n終於有一個人係講d相反意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無睇過叔本華既孤獨論？<br />\n有一排真係好無心情 又放暑假 於是同全世界既人隔絕<br />\n但個人就容易變得異常敏感, 精神萎靡<br />\n所以我覺得自己係不得不交朋友<br />\n就好似要取暖一樣<br />\n<br />\n與其話唔重視佢地<br />\n不如話係取暖既同時 同火保持一段距離<br />\n唔會灼傷自己"},{"pid":"57b0d86a859695b4b7debca2c7e555b794b7ff3c","tid":36571,"uid":62458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:42:50.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a766c053b74b0506d471c6eb688e23c9d7fd1f9","tid":36571,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"一樣無興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對所有人都係hi bye算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b755ef49aa6119364cf02a220bdbe3ab9c521a36","tid":36571,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"係自私, 無咩問題"},{"pid":"df9fded7baeac247f245389bc13c9d4f8657e605","tid":36571,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係自私, 無咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打details"},{"pid":"6a9398dff1e25e8f482cccfdc993d747f9c0f831","tid":36571,"uid":47321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"我同樓主完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平日自己出街唔會覺得寂寞<